('2MA', '2 Maccabees', 'Deuterocanon', 2, 'deuterocanonical', 'Second Temple (c. 124 BCE)', 'Greek (epitome of Jason of Cyrene''s 5-volume work)', 'Greek (epitome of Jason of Cyrene''s 5-volume work)', 0.88, ARRAY['Codex Sinaiticus (4th c.)','Codex Alexandrinus (5th c.)'], ARRAY['Catholic','Orthodox','Ethiopian'], NULL, 0, ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Parallel account to 1 Macc covering 180-161 BCE. More theological than 1 Macc.'),
