('PS2', 'Psalm 151', 'Deuterocanon', 2, 'deuterocanonical', 'Second Temple (2nd c. BCE or earlier)', 'Hebrew', 'Greek (LXX), Hebrew (DSS 11Q5)', 0.94, ARRAY['Hebrew: DSS 11Q5 (Psalms Scroll, 1st c. BCE)','Greek: LXX manuscripts','Syriac Peshitta'], ARRAY['Orthodox','Ethiopian'], NULL, 0, ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'David''s psalm after defeating Goliath. Hebrew DSS manuscript (11Q5) confirms antiquity.'),
